            <h2>Comics</h2>
            <p>Lots of people read comics. It is a great way to have fun and socialize in the meanwhile.
                would you like endless debates over which super hero is the strongest? Or which super power
                would suit you? Then check out these profiles, and you might just end up with Captain America in a room!
